menu_42021_1=
menu_42022_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Elder Brother, what is our next course of action?</font>
menu_42025_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Elder Brother, I</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" > will</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" > find Fang Biao. Have your troops guard the foot of the mountain to prevent an escape. If anyone but me comes down that path, you know what to do.</font>
menu_42026_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">Is that all you have to say?</font>
menu_42027_1=
menu_42028_1=
menu_42029_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">So Zhang Shijun is nothing but a disgraceful miscreant. This could mean he is the source of the recent disasters in the village. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff">I'll deal with that later. For now I need to find a way out of this valley.</font>
menu_42037_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >No. I appreciate the concern, Elder Brother, but I can make it back myself.</font>
menu_42038_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I hope the man who watched me fall off the cliff also got a promotion. </font>
menu_42039_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Did you remember your place when you cheated your masters and betrayed your colleague?</font>
menu_42040_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Yes he was killed, because you betrayed him!</font>
menu_42041_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >How did you know about that</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >?</font>
menu_42042_1=<font face="Default" color="#8fd6ef">(I'll have to endure this humiliation, for now.) </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff">It seems you will get your way, Flag Emissary Zhang.</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff">Hmph. Excuse me!</font>
