target_42258=<s>Go to Xingxiu Sect. You find Abbess Buji was attacked by Xingxiu Sect disciples. You tried to protect her but she was still injured and poisoned.
target_42263=<s>Go to Xingxiu Sect's highest point to use the poison. You got exposed by Xingxiu Sect disciple. Fight him and then report to Jiang Yici.
